See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomTabActivityHelper.ConnectionCallback
    A Callback for when the service is connected or disconnected.
    CustomTabActivityHelper.CustomTabFallback
    To be used as a fallback to open the Uri when Custom Tabs is not available.
    ServiceConnectionCallback
    Callback for events when connecting and disconnecting from Custom Tabs Service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomTabActivityHelper
    This is a helper class to manage the connection to the Custom Tabs Service.
    CustomTabsHelper
    Helper class for Custom Tabs.
    KeepAliveService
    Empty service used by the custom tab to bind to, raising the application's importance.
    ServiceConnection
    Implementation for the CustomTabsServiceConnection that avoids leaking the ServiceConnectionCallback
    WebViewFallback
    Fallback of customtab with a standard web view
